{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EXILED AND ABANDONED</strong> <br>Banished from your homeland, you awaken the dormant powers of necromancy within you. On a secluded forest clearing, you raise your shrine and repel wave after wave of heroic attackers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FIGHT</strong><br>Take the fight to your foes by engaging them head-on, or let your towers and skeletal legion do the heavy lifting. The battlefield is yours to command.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514820/extras/fight.gif?t=1739305522\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BUILD YOUR BASE</strong><br>Construct towers, fences, barracks, and a vast array of structures. Every placement is in your hands\u2014strategize and design the ultimate defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514820/extras/build_gif.gif?t=1739305522\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GATHER RESOURCES</strong> <br>Gather vital resources and grow your base. With each expansion, you strengthen your hold against increasingly formidable enemy waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514820/extras/gather_resources.gif?t=1739305522\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IMPROVE</strong><br>Earn experience with every encounter, unlock powerful perks, and refine your strategy to make each run better than the last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514820/extras/skelton_army.gif?t=1739305522\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739305522","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai